{"word":"ἀμυντέος","slug":"ἀμυντέος","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἀμυντέος</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:verbal Adjective'>verb. <a href='S:Adjective'>adj.</a></a> of <a href='S:ἀμύνω'><el>ἀμύνω</el></a>\n<p/><i>one must assist</i>, <a href='S:cum'>c.</a> <a href='S:dative'>dat.</a> <a href='S:person, personal'>pers.</a>, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b>; so <a href='S:plural'>pl.</a> <el>ἀμυντέα</el>, <b><a href='S:Sophocles'>Soph.</a></b><p/>"}]}